        <p begin="00:01:48.919" end="00:01:51.420" tts:direction="ltr">This is a fairly small backpack.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:51.420" end="00:01:56.899" tts:direction="ltr">I might just be going to Crimson or on
<br />another a short day hike.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:56.899" end="00:02:00.500" tts:direction="ltr">But I've always got to make sure that my
<br />pack is ready to go.</p>
        <p begin="00:02:00.500" end="00:02:05.279" tts:direction="ltr">Just like on a adventure here in data
