        <p begin="00:02:05.279" end="00:02:07.700" tts:direction="ltr">you have to start off with that purpose.</p>
        <p begin="00:02:07.700" end="00:02:18.359" tts:direction="ltr">Our purpose metaphor is going to be R
<br />let's see what I've got, O map.</p>
        <p begin="00:02:18.359" end="00:02:20.380" tts:direction="ltr">Here I've got the Logan,</p>
        <p begin="00:02:20.380" end="00:02:23.340" tts:direction="ltr">Bear River Range right there in our
<br />backyard.</p>
        <p begin="00:02:23.340" end="00:02:27.379" tts:direction="ltr">It's got all of the topography and
