        <p begin="00:02:27.379" end="00:02:31.899" tts:direction="ltr">But what I'm going to need to do is
<br />identify my purpose,</p>
        <p begin="00:02:31.899" end="00:02:35.959" tts:direction="ltr">and that needs to be in a single sentence
<br />because in</p>
        <p begin="00:02:35.959" end="00:02:40.440" tts:direction="ltr">this day and age of communication
