        <p begin="00:02:40.440" end="00:02:43.079" tts:direction="ltr">we really have to focus and really put a
<br />lot of</p>
        <p begin="00:02:43.079" end="00:02:47.020" tts:direction="ltr">time energy and effort to creating a
<br />single sentence.</p>
        <p begin="00:02:47.020" end="00:02:49.670" tts:direction="ltr">So Why do we communicate?</p>
        <p begin="00:02:49.670" end="00:02:52.089" tts:direction="ltr">Clearly, it's because we want to be able</p>
