        <p begin="00:03:00.510" end="00:03:03.589" tts:direction="ltr">Now, what that does is it really defines</p>
        <p begin="00:03:03.589" end="00:03:07.529" tts:direction="ltr">your purpose and what you hope to
<br />accomplish.</p>
        <p begin="00:03:07.529" end="00:03:14.610" tts:direction="ltr">Now, I've seen multi pronged purposes and
<br />they do not often succeed.</p>
        <p begin="00:03:14.610" end="00:03:16.949" tts:direction="ltr">The purposes that are single sentence</p>
        <p begin="00:03:16.949" end="00:03:20.514" tts:direction="ltr">typically are ones that are doable,
<br />they're achievable.</p>
        <p begin="00:03:20.514" end="00:03:22.899" tts:direction="ltr">Because you are limited to this sentence.</p>
        <p begin="00:03:22.899" end="00:03:26.879" tts:direction="ltr">Now, don't do a sentence with</p>
        <p begin="00:03:26.879" end="00:03:31.159" tts:direction="ltr">all the dashes and semi colons and things
<br />like that,</p>
        <p begin="00:03:31.159" end="00:03:33.599" tts:direction="ltr">but we're trying to really focus in on a
<br />single sentence.</p>
        <p begin="00:03:33.599" end="00:03:37.140" tts:direction="ltr">We're thinking about, are we trying to
<br />inform our audience,</p>
        <p begin="00:03:37.140" end="00:03:39.820" tts:direction="ltr">are we trying to persuade or convince our
<br />audience?</p>
        <p begin="00:03:39.820" end="00:03:42.839" tts:direction="ltr">Are we trying to motivate or inspire them,</p>
        <p begin="00:03:42.839" end="00:03:45.299" tts:direction="ltr">or are we simply trying to instruct your
<br />audience?</p>
        <p begin="00:03:45.299" end="00:03:46.839" tts:direction="ltr">It's important to know where we're</p>
        <p begin="00:03:46.839" end="00:03:52.290" tts:direction="ltr">starting then that will help us with our
<br />purpose.</p>
        <p begin="00:03:52.290" end="00:03:54.799" tts:direction="ltr">Most of the time, we're looking to inform
<br />or</p>
        <p begin="00:03:54.799" end="00:03:57.180" tts:direction="ltr">persuade specifically in business.</p>
        <p begin="00:03:57.180" end="00:04:02.159" tts:direction="ltr">We're trying to persuade them to some an
<br />action item that we're hoping to get.</p>
        <p begin="00:04:02.159" end="00:04:06.639" tts:direction="ltr">Here are some examples of some single
